## Tips
- Start with option 2 (Compare All Strategies) to see what works best
- Use shorter periods (30-90 days) for quick testing
- Save successful configurations to the library
- Portfolio backtesting requires sufficient data (30+ days minimum)
- Check Help menu (option 30) for detailed guidance

---

## Troubleshooting

**"Insufficient data" error**: Try a longer time period (60-90 days minimum)

**Network errors**: Check internet connection, Yahoo Finance may be throttling

**Permission denied**: Run `chmod +x START.sh` or use Option 1

**Import errors**: Ensure all dependencies installed:
```bash
pip install yfinance pandas numpy scikit-learn matplotlib seaborn
```

